数:597\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,4,context deadline exceeded,出现次数:586\naiops-k8s-03,frontend,frontend-0,frontend-0,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,4,context deadline exceeded,出现次数:296\naiops-k8s-03,frontend,frontend-0,frontend-0,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,4,stream terminated by RST_STREAM with error code: CANCEL,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,4,stream terminated by RST_STREAM with error code: CANCEL,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,4,stream terminated by RST_STREAM with error code: CANCEL,出现次数:1\n", "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-11T15:10:55Z to 2025-06-11T15:31:55Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-11 15:10:55+00:00 to 2025-06-11 15:31:55+00:00"}, "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取的链路追踪数据，我现在进行详细分析。从数据中可以看到明显的异常模式，特别是广告服务(AdService)相关的调用出现了严重的超时问题。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"frontend->adservice\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\", \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\", \"checkoutservice->emailservice\", \"cartservice->redis\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"广告服务调用延迟从正常5.4秒激增至500秒，延迟倍数约92倍，出现大量'context deadline exceeded'超时错误(共1481次)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ShippingService调用延迟从13.9秒增至80.9秒，延迟倍数约5.8倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"PaymentService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PaymentService调用延迟从12.8秒增至69.5秒，延迟倍数约5.4倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis操作延迟从1.4秒激增至77.7秒，延迟倍数约57倍，影响购物车服务\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现分析：**\n\n1. **AdService是主要根因**: 三个前端实例(frontend-0,1,2)调用AdService都出现了严重的超时问题，延迟增加了92倍，并且有大量\"context deadline exceeded\"错误，表明AdService可能完全不可用或响应极慢。\n\n2. **检查流程服务链受影响**: CheckoutService调用的下游服务(Shipping、Payment、Email)都出现了显著延迟，表明整个订单处理流程受到影响。\n\n3. **Redis存储层异常**: CartService对Redis的操作延迟异常增加，可能影响了购物车功能的正常使用。\n\n4. **错误传播路径**: AdService的故障通过前端服务传播到整个系统，影响了用户界面的广告展示和后续的购物流程。\n\n建议进一步调查AdService的具体状态和资源使用情况，这很可能是本次系统故障的主要根因。", "log_analysis_findings": "根据日志数据分析，以下是关键发现和根因假设：\n\n### 关键错误模式\n1. **`frontend` 服务频繁报错**：\n   - 错误信息：`failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded`\n   - 出现频次：非常高（总计超过 1000 次）。\n   - 这表明 `frontend` 服务在调用 `adservice` 时超时。\n\n2. **`adservice` 服务异常**：\n   - 日志中多次出现 `Agent failed to start!` 和 `java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once`。\n   - 此外，`adservice` 的 `getRandomAds` 方法被频繁触发（`AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749654655` 相关日志出现 1484 次），可能与性能问题或配置错误有关。\n\n3. **其他错误**：\n   - 少量 `stream terminated by RST_STREAM with error code: CANCEL` 错误，表明部分请求被主动取消。\n\n### 根因假设\n- **`adservice` 服务是根因**：\n  - 多个 `frontend` 实例同时抱怨 `adservice` 服务超时。\n  - `adservice` 自身日志显示其代理启动失败，且 `getRandomAds` 方法可能因性能问题无法及时响应。\n\n### 输出结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"DeadlineExceeded\",\n    \"context deadline exceeded\",\n    \"Agent failed to start\",\n    \"java.lang.Exception\",\n    \"AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749654655\",\n    \"stream terminated by RST_STREAM\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Agent failed to start and performance issues in getRandomAds method causing DeadlineExceeded errors\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Agent failed to start! and AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749654655 execute()\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于获取的指标数据，我现在进行故障分析。让我分析异常指标并识别根本原因。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"io_util\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend服务响应时间异常飙升，rrt从11868.34ms增加到38698.82ms（增长106%），rrt_max从195508ms增加到603788ms（增长102%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0的rrt中位数变化率1.0612，p99变化率1.1689；rrt_max中位数变化率1.0216\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend服务响应时间显著增加，rrt从12134.22ms增加到36140.78ms（增长99%），rrt_max从242468ms增加到609758ms（增长86%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-1的rrt中位数变化率0.9946，p99变化率1.0988；rrt_max中位数变化率0.862\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend服务响应时间严重恶化，rrt从12175.62ms增加到36015.48ms（增长99%），rrt_max从234163.5ms增加到611115ms（增长89%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-2的rrt中位数变化率0.9894，p99变化率1.0896；rrt_max中位数变化率0.8919\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"支付服务响应时间异常，rrt_max从1689.5ms增加到1745ms，p99值从3098.97ms飙升到58098.4ms（增长1797%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"paymentservice-1的rrt_max p99变化率1.7974，表明存在严重性能问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"购物车服务响应时间异常，rrt_max从3037ms减少到2696ms，但p99值从8296.73ms飙升到75907.2ms（增长605%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-2的rrt_max p99变化率1.6059，表明存在严重的尾部延迟问题\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**关键发现**：\n1. **前端服务全面故障**：所有frontend实例（frontend-0、frontend-1、frontend-2）的响应时间都出现了严重恶化，rrt指标增长约100%，表明这是系统级故障。\n\n2. **下游服务性能问题**：paymentservice-1和cartservice-2表现出严重的尾部延迟问题，p99响应时间分别增长1797%和605%，这可能是导致前端服务整体性能下降的原因。\n\n3. **错误率变化**：虽然error_ratio和client_error_ratio的变化相对较小，但checkoutservice-2的错误率有轻微上升。\n\n4. **系统资源正常**：node_memory_usage_rate和io_util指标变化不大，排除了系统资源瓶颈的可能性。\n\n**根本原因推测**：支付服务（paymentservice-1）和购物车服务（cartservice-2）的性能问题可能是导致前端服务整体响应时间恶化的主要原因。"}
